{{作品名称|name=''El agente topo''|cn=名侦探赛大爷|hk=臨時偵探無限耆|lang=es}}是2020年多国合拍纪录片，由{{link-en|梅特·阿尔贝蒂|Maite Alberdi}}执导。影片讲述年迈的私家侦探赛尔吉奥卧底调查养老院的经历。影片于2020年1月25日在{{tsl|en|2020 Sundance Film Festival|2020年圣丹斯电影节}}世界纪录片竞赛单元首映。在[[第93屆奧斯卡金像獎|第93屆奧斯卡金像獎]]上，为智利选送参与[[奥斯卡最佳國際影片獎|奥斯卡最佳國際影片獎]]竞逐的作品<ref name="Chile">{{cite web |url=https://www.fotech.cl/el-agente-topo-sera-el-representante-de-chile-en-los-premios-oscar/2020/11/19/ |title="El Agente Topo" será el representante de Chile en los premios Oscar |work=Fotech |date=2020-11-19 |access-date=2020-11-19 |archive-date=2020-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119123447/https://www.fotech.cl/el-agente-topo-sera-el-representante-de-chile-en-los-premios-oscar/2020/11/19/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但止步于最终15强名单<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2021/film/news/oscars-shortlist-2021-makeup-visual-score-song-international-documentary-1234904174/ |title=Oscars Shortlists Announced in Nine Categories |work=Variety |first=Clayton |last=Davis |date=2021-02-09 |access-date=2021-02-10 |archive-date=2021-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209230223/https://variety.com/2021/film/news/oscars-shortlist-2021-makeup-visual-score-song-international-documentary-1234904174/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最终获[[奥斯卡最佳纪录片奖|最佳纪录片]]提名。

== 发行 ==
影片于2020年1月25日在[[圣丹斯电影节|圣丹斯电影节]]全球首映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sundance-2020-unveils-female-powered-lineup-taylor-swift-gloria-steinem-films-1259538?|title=Sundance Unveils Female-Powered Lineup Featuring Taylor Swift, Gloria Steinem, Abortion Road Trip Drama|website=The Hollywood Reporter|first=Tatiana|last=Siegel|date=2019-12-04|access-date=2020-12-23|archive-date=2019-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208151948/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sundance-2020-unveils-female-powered-lineup-taylor-swift-gloria-steinem-films-1259538|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sundance.org/projects/the-mole-agent|title=The Mole Agent|website=Sundance Film Festival|access-date=2020-12-23|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120065526/https://www.sundance.org/projects/the-mole-agent|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年8月，{{tsl|en|Gravitas Ventures|Gravitas Ventures}}买下影片美国发行权，定于9月1日上映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ramascreen.com/gravitas-ventures-acquires-documentary-the-mole-agent/|title=Gravitas Ventures Acquires Documentary THE MOLE AGENT|website=Rama Screen|author=Rama|date=2020-08-05|access-date=2020-12-23|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129212310/https://www.ramascreen.com/gravitas-ventures-acquires-documentary-the-mole-agent/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年1月25日，美国[[公共广播电视公司|公共广播电视公司]]《{{tsl|en|POV (TV series)|POV (电视节目)|POV}}》节目播出该片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pbs.org/pov/watch/moleagent/|title=The Mole Agent|website=PBS|access-date=2020-12-23|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129155301/http://www.pbs.org/pov/watch/moleagent/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年12月10日，影片在荷兰上映，由Cinema Delicatessen发行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cinemadelicatessen.nl/film/the-mole-agent/|title=The Mole Agent|website=Cinema Delicatessen|access-date=2020-12-23|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129182055/http://www.cinemadelicatessen.nl/film/the-mole-agent/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 评价 ==
影片在[[汇总媒体|汇总媒体]][[烂番茄|烂番茄]]上有51条评论，新鲜度94%，平均得分7.5/10。网站共识写道：“《名侦探赛大爷》猛地提醒观众建立新的人际关系、展开新冒险永远不会迟，温馨之余也不乏幽默<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_mole_agent|title=The Mole Agent|website=Rotten Tomatoes|publisher=Fandango Media|access-date=2021-01-29|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209045714/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_mole_agent|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]收录13条评论，平均得分69/100，表示“普遍好评”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-mole-agent|title=The Mole Agent Reviews|website=Metacritic|publisher=CBS Interactive|access-date=2021-01-29|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125203835/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-mole-agent|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的格伦·肯尼（Glenn Kenny）给出正面评价：“片中的人让人很感动，传达出的效果感人肺腑、具人文关怀且值得注意<ref>{{cite web |date= 2020-09-01 |last1= Kenny |first1= Glenn |title= 'The Mole Agent' Review: Undercover, Where You Least Expect Him |url= https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/01/movies/the-mole-agent-review.html |website= The New York Times |accessdate= 2021-04-01 |archive-date= 2021-03-30 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210330141346/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/01/movies/the-mole-agent-review.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。”{{tsl|en|RogerEbert.com|RogerEbert.com}}的尼克·艾伦（Nick Allen）打出3/4星的评价，认为影片的成功之处在于它的柔情，生动地告诉我们社会是多么容易遗忘老人<ref>{{cite web|date= 2020-09-01|last1= Allen|first1= Nick|title= The Mole Agent|url= https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-mole-agent-movie-review-2020|website= RogerEbert.com|accessdate= 2021-04-01|archive-date= 2021-01-16|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210116174311/https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-mole-agent-movie-review-2020|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

